Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  会长就没有不困的早上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚睡了几个小时？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三小时？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer一直都是这么说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「睡眠不足可是美容的大敌」哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  挚爱的Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那如丝般润滑的肌肤  I wanna touch you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明爱理他们马上就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有大人物要来视察嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  诗织阿姨  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这是要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  休息日加班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  你就是KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨  佳织的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really！？  不是sister吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  爱理  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  难得来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们慢慢玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  都买来了哦  牛奶和鸡蛋还有黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这些就行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  别的都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文化节上用的点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为必须提前一天先做好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做些简单的烤制点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要做  就认真尝试看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭是佳织亲手做的这一点  粉丝们肯定会络绎不绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角不是天象仪吗  咖啡厅只是顺带的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都是主角啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出来的点心也是越好吃越好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你会做点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好失礼啊  别看我这样手还是很灵巧的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没有做过而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听着佳织的指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是佳织  你手腕的伤没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像平常一样用的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  结说一会她也会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川要来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过凪沙学姐好像有事来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉要变热闹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结知道来我家的路么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且把地图发给凪沙学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西有必要非得自己做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天象仪什么的  店里买个不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  这样说的话点心也可以去店里买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不就没有存在的价值了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  累死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了连半小时都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长这种平凡的活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  反正开始就没指望过你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure…get！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的嘛  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先做的已经烤好啦  想让你们尝一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸展运动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Stretch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scone！这玩意看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好试验品一号刚烤好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结也来尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去倒点红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是走着来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为天气非常好顺便能光合作用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是日光浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜  要是凪沙学姐也在的话全员就能凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪沙学姐好像过一会也能来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谁让你随便开始吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不是要试吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只是偷吃而已吧  不给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  还有好多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织是Angel啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我  做的真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正大部分都是佳织做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也撒了粉  做了形状的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个能成为天文学会的招牌商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  先定下来把这个加入菜单  接下来还要再加几个别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来想试着做下曲奇饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结能来一起帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结会烧饭做菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:07:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要用那个来开星座的小洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  用微妙的大小区别来调整通光量从而再现星空的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要小心谨慎才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要开多少个洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少个呢  肉眼能看到的星星大概有数千个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus  好蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤好要多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三四分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会能借用一些时间吗  有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  在我面前不能说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等那边烤好了再说行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那就一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟  这个模特的腰部曲线和Jennifer一模一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  尾宿八做的太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就行了嘛  那种东西没人会在意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！说不定就会有对观星非常感兴趣的人来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有更好用的工具就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色也想好好再现一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  烤的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  毕竟第一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？结呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  是不是去厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后一定会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  结  曲奇烤好了哦  来尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  结也说好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  我也再来一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  成功了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦  这边只能我自己做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试验品二号做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  等死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像形状各异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是试验品了啊  快吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天应该能做的差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要踩那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往乏味的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也尝尝味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木同学喜欢秋山同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么突然问这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果未来  这样的生活如此持续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和奏只不过是普通的青梅竹马而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  难道你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室里的红茶差不多要喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该补充一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都能记着真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  爱理回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏说要出去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要买些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以干脆就出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想尝试更多种类的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要去买点材料回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要什么只要说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会帮你们买回来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去买也很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就去地下的食品区了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是要买杂货  大概是在上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KENNY能来这边帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还提不了重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要买什么啊  准备买那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是很多东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结就过去帮一下奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要好好盯着奏不要浪费钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当我小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了我刚才说的要买红茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把他们两个凑到一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么原因的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是活动室里常喝的那个你精挑细选的红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  马上就要喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是结告诉我  到时候还得特地再过来买
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这些就齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:13:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  和佳织的挺像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  让你陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么有意思的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  这个看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No money
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给我忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的分你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}噢  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Thanks so  so very very very much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在一起真的很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个磅蛋糕怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责的已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就到这里负责试吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是有多饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫我还处在身体疯长的阶段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去帮秋山同学的忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去了也没什么事干的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那结你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  看上去不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看能不能帮你点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同学你真的很喜欢星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只记得小时候看到的星空漂亮得令我感动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听别人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在地面上看见的星辰的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很久以前发出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从遥远的宇宙历经漫长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才终于抵达这里的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处女座银河距离地球是239万光年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所见到的光是239万年前的光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,239万年  无论是时间上还是距离上都让人难以想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个从后面照一下试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有加上颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是夏季的星座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后你想起些什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没必要着急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候总会想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得某个人的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张侧脸虽然在微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却又非常的忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是古川的亲人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是亲人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太清楚  不过对古川来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是个和你有很深的关联的人物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:18:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才古川说话的时候显得很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那个人对我来说应该是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一二三等星都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  我是结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡傻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之临时组装完之后去看看那边的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  佳织来过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在说这句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底选哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like them all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是会很辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  你觉得天象仪真的能吸引来顾客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  大家期待的只是佳织的女仆装和亲手做的点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得天文学会的会长说这个是不是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  KENNY偶尔也会说些正经话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个看上去都很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我姑且也帮了忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华宫学姐也试吃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  什么都没能帮到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么  这话凪沙一说听上去好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是来接结的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是试装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过天象仪也已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  关灯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是奏做出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  底座是KENNY做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的部分结也来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然用名字称呼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  没什么大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  比起这个  还是快看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  那就是夏季大三角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来天文宅发挥本领了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大三角的织女星虽然看上去是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在夏季南边天空上天蝎座的心宿二却被称为红超巨星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散发着红色的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么会有颜色的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为表面温度的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心宿二大约在3500度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的织女星大约是9500度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提  太阳的表面温度大约是6000度左右
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  谢谢你来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只做到三等星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少在文化节之前能完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛  接下来才是重头戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更小的四五等星的洞差不多要钻3000个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等级是依靠光亮来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但实际的亮度和观测时的亮度还是有区别的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫绝对星等和视星等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个天象仪总之…
