Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:31.30,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}怎么了  慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.14,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}还剩十分种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.04,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}佳织不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:33.79,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}不能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:35.56,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}明天见
